dimensions.name: Country
descriptions: List of countries for where events originate

formulas.name: IX Fill Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[vadr]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_served])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[vadr]))

formulas.name: IX Win Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_served]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[valid_wins])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_served]))

formulas.name: Video Completion Rate(VCR)
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[media_plays]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[completed_views])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[media_plays]))

formulas.name: CTR
formulas.dax_expression: (SUM('CSM Data'[clicks]) + SUM('CSM Data'[custom_clicks]))/SUM('CSM Data'[ads_rendered])

formulas.name: eCPM
formulas.dax_expression: 1000*(IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(), SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[total_burn])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])))

formulas.name: IX Render Rate
descriptions: Ad Impressions Rendered/ IX Wins (If Header Bidding then Valid Wins, if MCO Ads Served)
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[IX_Wins]) < 1, BLANK(), 
sum('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[IX_Wins]))

formulas.name: CAS Win Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF([cas fills para] < 1, BLANK(),
[cas win para]/[cas fills para])

formulas.name: CAS Fill Rate
formulas.dax_expression: SUM('CSM Data'[cas_fills])/SUM('CSM Data'[cas_forwards])

formulas.name: CAS Render Rate
descriptions: Ad Impressions Rendered/ Ad Impressions Served
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(sum('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_served]) < 1, BLANK(), 
sum('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])/sum('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_served]))

formulas.name: Inmobi Margin Rate
formulas.dax_expression: SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[inmobi_margins])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[total_burn])

formulas.name: EC CTR
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[companion_ad_clicks])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: End Card Render Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])<1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[companions_ad_rendered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: EV CTR
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[evc_triggered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: Load Errors
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called]) <1, BLANK(), 
1- (SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called])))

formulas.name: Media Click Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[media_clicks])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: rCPM
formulas.dax_expression:
IF([vadr Para] < 1, BLANK(), 
1000*(sum('Exchange daily Demand'[total_burn])/[vadr Para]))

formulas.name: ATC Pass Through
formulas.dax_expression: DIVIDE([vadr Para],[SVADR Para])

formulas.name: End Card Click Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])<1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[companion_ad_clicks])/ SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: EV Clicks/EV Enabled
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[evc_enabled])<1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[evc_triggered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[evc_enabled]))

formulas.name: Show Rate
formulas.dax_expression:
if([Ad Impressions Loaded IX]<1 , BLANK(),
DIVIDE([Ad Impressions Shown IX], [Ad Impressions Loaded IX]))

formulas.name: Rendered/Shown
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]))

formulas.name: Sum of Total Burn
formulas.dax_expression: SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[total_burn])

formulas.name: Viewable/Shown
formulas.dax_expression:
if(sum('SDK Version Demand'[ad_impressions_shown])<1, BLANK(),
sum('SDK Version Demand'[mrc_viewable])/sum('SDK Version Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]))

formulas.name: EV CTR
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[evc_triggered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: Media Plays/Rendered
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])<1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[media_plays])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: Ads Called/Forwards
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[cas_forwards])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called]))

formulas.name: Ads Loaded/Forwards
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[cas_forwards])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded]))

formulas.name: Rendered/Forwards
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[cas_forwards])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered]))

formulas.name: Shown/Forwards
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[cas_forwards])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]))

formulas.name: Viewable/Forwards
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[cas_forwards])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_shown]))

formulas.name: Ads Loaded/Ads Called
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called]) < 1, BLANK(),
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_load_called]))

formulas.name: Rendered/Ad Loaded
formulas.dax_expression:
IF(SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded]) < 1, BLANK(), 
SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])/SUM('Exchange daily Demand'[ad_impressions_loaded]))

formulas.name: Click Conversions
formulas.dax_expression:
if(sum('Exchange daily Demand'[clicks])<1 , blank(),
 sum('Exchange daily Demand'[landings])/sum('Exchange daily Demand'[clicks]))

formulas.name: EV Enabled/Rendered
Valid Wins/Fills
Rendered/Fills
formulas.dax_expression:
if(sum('SDK Version Demand'[cas_fills])<1, BLANK(),
(sum('SDK Version Demand'[ads_rendered]))/sum('SDK Version Demand'[cas_fills]))

formulas.name: Supply_CTR
formulas.dax_expression: sum('Exchange daily Demand'[clicks])/sum('Exchange daily Demand'[ads_rendered])
